  "task_intent": "Scientific-answer test: predict the experimental binding-effect direction for barnase D39A in the barnase-barstar complex (PDB 1BRS) from MD-derived evidence. Run short comparative MD of the WT complex and the D39A mutant complex, populate metrics.md_analysis with quantitative interface differences (\u0394interface SASA, \u0394 inter-chain contact count, \u0394 hydrogen-bond count, \u0394 salt-bridge count, \u0394 water occupancy at the interface, etc.), populate evidence_report.evidence.md_metrics, and report effect.direction with calibrated confidence and explicit limitations. Literature citations are admissible for confidence calibration only; the direction itself must be defended by the MD numbers.",
